com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn

Class PoolingLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.RegisteredObjectBase
        • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.LayerBase
          • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn.PoolingLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MultiPrecision<PoolingLayer>, Layer, ReferenceCounting, Serializable

    public class PoolingLayer
extends LayerBase
implements MultiPrecision<PoolingLayer>
    The standard image-pixel pooling layer. Using a configurable stride and window size, reduces pixels using either the Max or Avg operation.
